    "review": "I find this game really addictive, enjoyable and fun. Once I start playing I don't want to stop.\n\nI enjoy trying to find fish and sort out the Sushi shop.\nHowever I felt the Sea People content was the weakest and kind of boring, annoying and game would be better without it compared to everything else. I don't like them and wish we could have a option to nuke them out of the game.\nIt's also annoying that there is a limited save. Can only save when not diving. I ended up in the glacial passage, it was taking too long and you can't just exit the game so had to close it in taskmanager as I had other things to do and don't like leaving games running.\n\nI disliked having a 2nd branch of sushi shop to organise. No thanks, I just ignored it as I prefer to focus on one.\n\nBecause of content I don't like I'd rate this game 7/10 and not 8 or higher.\n",
