    "language": "english",
    "review": "This is such a great game! It's a mix of rogue-lite, farming sim (just a tiny bit), and bar management. Main game consists of 2 game modes: catch a fish, and then serve clients in your sushi bar. Catching fish is a unique game experience, where you swim in a 2D space, but can go in any give direction. You have to gather ingredients for you dishes, which are not limited only by fish. \nIn bar you have to manage your staff, menu with dishes, and serve clients. Once the bar is closed, you get money, which let you upgrade your gear to get better fish, to earn more money, to upgrade your diving gear even more. This gameplay loop is addictive and fun. \nDave the Diver also has a simple, but short and funny story to get you involved in the process even more and give you a goal. The game gets a bit more grindy and boring in the late game, but the story is close to an end at this point.\nOverall, I can recommend this game almost to every person.",
